* PyCOBOL Error Test File — Tests Lexical Error Detection
* This file intentionally contains lexical errors

IDENTIFICATION DIVISION
PROGRAM-ID: ErrorTest
AUTHOR: CS Student

DATA DIVISION
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION
    01 employee_name    PIC A(30)
    01 salary           PIC 9(7)V99
    01 bad_pic          PIC Z(5)
    01 department       PIC A(20)

PROCEDURE DIVISION

# Test 1: Unclosed string literal
employee_name = "Ahmed Khan
salary = 75000

# Test 2: Unknown/invalid characters
total = salary + bonus @ tax
price = 100 $ 50

# Test 3: Another unclosed string
DISPLAY "Hello World

# Test 4: Valid code to show recovery works
COMPUTE bonus = salary * 0.15
DISPLAY "This is fine"

STOP RUN
